{"id":"projects/baby-tracking-app","title":"Privacy-Friendly Baby Tracking App (CS 461 capstone)","type":"projects","html":"<blockquote>\n<p>Stub. <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/osu\">OSU</a> <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/cs-461\">CS 461</a> Group 27 capstone — cross-platform mobile baby-tracking app architected <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/local-first-storage\">local first</a> with opt-in cloud backup. Counter-positioned against incumbent baby-trackers that route infant data through third-party clouds. AES-256 encryption, <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/react-native\">React Native</a>, <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/gemini\">Gemini</a> API for ML features. Compliance scope: GDPR, COPPA, CCPA, HIPAA-aligned (not mandated).</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Team: <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/bryant-shitabata\">Bryant</a>, <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/jacob-cocheu\">Jacob</a>, <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/sonny-box\">Sonny</a>, Yahir.</p>\n<p>Source: <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2024-12-04-requirements-document-2\">2024 12 04 requirements document 2</a></p>\n<p>Architectural kinship: <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"projects/rankett\">rankett</a> (private-by-default), <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"projects/irl-lore\">irl lore</a> (private journal), <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/biometric-privacy-tradeoff\">biometric privacy tradeoff</a> (the underlying instinct).</p>\n","related":[{"id":"concepts/biometric-privacy-tradeoff","label":"Biometric Privacy Tradeoff"},{"id":"entities/bryant-shitabata","label":"Bryant Shitabata"},{"id":"entities/cs-461","label":"CS 461 (OSU Software Engineering capstone)"},{"id":"summaries/2024-12-04-requirements-document-2","label":"CS 461 Privacy-Friendly Baby Tracking App PRD (12/4/24)"},{"id":"entities/gemini","label":"Gemini"},{"id":"projects/irl-lore","label":"IRL Lore"},{"id":"entities/jacob-cocheu","label":"Jacob Cocheu"},{"id":"concepts/local-first-storage","label":"Local-first storage"},{"id":"entities/osu","label":"Oregon State University (OSU)"},{"id":"projects/rankett","label":"Rankett"},{"id":"entities/react-native","label":"React Native"},{"id":"entities/simplebaby","label":"SimpleBaby"},{"id":"summaries/2025-03-16-screenshot-2025-03-16-at-7-01-47-pm-c70df294","label":"SimpleBaby — first-child onboarding"},{"id":"summaries/2025-03-16-screenshot-2025-03-16-at-7-03-48-pm-fceecb78","label":"SimpleBaby — Logs/Trackers tab layout"},{"id":"summaries/2025-03-16-screenshot-2025-03-16-at-6-50-56-pm-fe7f3d85","label":"SimpleBaby — welcome / sign-in screen"},{"id":"entities/sonny-box","label":"Sonny Box"}]}
